间就给驾驶员预留了几秒钟的时间，甚至是一秒两秒。 我不知道其他驾驶员的反应速度是多少，反正我肯定是反应不过来的。 可我想不明白的是，智驾不就应该在这种紧急时刻来保命的吗？以它的反应速度来主动刹车，不比人的反应速度快吗？ 为什么还要当甩手掌柜呢？ 难不成就是为了避免责任。 我理解的智驾逻辑应该是 1.驾驶员主动要求智驾接管的时候，智驾应当首先判断外部环境是否满足智驾的要求，速度，路况，驾驶时长等。 或者就直接明确要求，速度高于多少，不允许智驾。 2.智驾要求驾驶员接管的时候，要强制，而不是提醒。而在智驾结束到驾驶员接管的这段时间内（可能就一秒两秒），智驾还要继续工作，例如刹车、变道等一系列的操作。"},"attached_info":"CkoIq4Luy/L5nZVgEAMaCTExNDI5MTIzNCCRu7K/BjAAOMQBQBByEzE4OTA3MDg2OTg2Njc2NTEzODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-601c1bc0c17a7ea58246c0e66a1bdd7b_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1743895158.93928","card_id":"Q_1887561347849490706","target":{"id":1887561347849490700,"title":"为什么很多网文大神强调‘前三章定生死’？读者耐心真的只剩3章了吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1887561347849490706","type":"question","created":1742809694,"answer_count":131,"follower_count":190,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[521],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在短视频时代，网文的“快节奏”是否已从10章压缩到3章？慢热型作品的成功是否已经过去或者只是特例？"},"attached_info":"CkoIq4Luy/L5nZVgEAMaCTExNDE0OTM3NSDe1IS/BjAAOL4BQBFyEzE4ODc1NjEzNDc4NDk0OTA3MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-903c098c2279fade6977d360d516dc38_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1743895158.94241","card_id":"Q_501886908","target":{"id":501886908,"title":"《天国王朝》伊贝林男爵才100户，真有这么少的男爵领吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/501886908","type":"question","created":1637966373,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":53,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[10813,29844,189000]